definitions.definition: A British or Irish nobleman next in rank above a viscount and below a marquess ; equivalent to a European count . A female using the style is termed a countess .
Any of various nymphalid butterflies of the genus Tanaecia . Other butterflies in this genus are called counts and viscounts .
